{"tid":1547420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［掛羊頭賣狗肉］你班人開twitter根本唔係文宣","createTime":"2019-09-06T16:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T08:51:45.000Z","uid":137615,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"42743dca77e239bfd75e26d197b2e3ddbefa13da","tid":1547420,"uid":137615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"用左twitter幾年，好開心香港終於有人用<br />\n<br />\n但我見而家d accounts/tweets個個都係呃followers<br />\n貼張女仔相 hashtag晒hongkongfollowback standwithhongkong 話自己唔夠followers唔夠retweet又盛 好難文宣<br />\n<br />\n結果呢堆人就淨係識retweet<br />\n仲要tweets全部中文<br />\n我心諗你點文宣呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實真心，新開twitter文宣未必要多followers<br />\n你去d news/representatives accounts comment/retweet，其他外國人就睇到<br />\n多d同外國人交流 先有文宣效果</span><br />\n一堆自己人互follow互retweet 圍爐取暖 冇意思<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前線為我地食緊彈，捱緊棍，你班人掛住文宣既口號呃followers呃retweets你良心話過唔過意得去？</span><br />\n<br />\n最後，不分化，不割蓆，想文宣既真心文宣唔該"},{"pid":"26214a9700079ec23a8fe8300621ca4b6a686ba7","tid":1547420,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 終極文宣 對準政權 全民抗共</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09f98a8b21c8395d2b6ea4c24fb399e6c49caca4","tid":1547420,"uid":213352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Yw7YiF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Yw7YiF.jpg&h=e6c84b70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日呀！冇人講呀 機場見</span>"},{"pid":"4f656f4aef800d03af5e61ddc5900